snippet.title: GoldenEye 007 – Xbox Game Pass Launch Trailer
snippet.description: GoldenEye 007 is back! Relive the classic '90s FPS, or discover its charms for the first time, in this faithful recreation for Xbox consoles including new achievements and 4K resolution. Play now via Rare Replay (digital copy) or Xbox Game Pass on Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S or Xbox Cloud Gaming.
